name: FDO Toolbox
tagline: A multi-purpose tool for working with geospatial data
body:
### About FDO Toolbox

FDO Toolbox is an multi-purpose geospatial tool to create, analyse, process and manage spatial data. It is written in C# and uses the [Feature Data Objects (FDO)](http://fdo.osgeo.org) API

FDO Toolbox (1.1 and newer) requires [.net Framework 4.0](http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=17718). Older releases require [.net Framework 2.0 SP2](http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=1639)

Disclaimer: Know what you are doing before trying this on production-quality geospatial data.
